---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Book a Free Call - taxomade" description="Book a free consultation with taxomade to discuss your relocation and tax setup in Southern Europe.">
  <main class="pt-32 pb-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      
      <!-- Hero Section -->
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <span class="inline-block py-1 px-3 rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">
          Free Consultation
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-6 tracking-tight">
          Let's talk about your setup.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          Just pick a time that suits you. In our call, we'll take the time to understand your situation and goals, then map out a tailored solution and the right local network for you.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
        
        <!-- Left/Main Column: Calendly Embed -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-2">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden" style="min-height: 700px;">
            <!-- Calendly inline widget begin -->
            <div class="calendly-inline-widget" data-url="https://calendly.com/taxomade/intro-call?hide_gdpr_banner=1&background_color=ffffff&text_color=0f172a&primary_color=1e3a8a" style="min-width:320px;height:700px;"></div>
            <script type="text/javascript" src="https://assets.calendly.com/assets/external/widget.js" async></script>
            <!-- Calendly inline widget end -->
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs text-center text-slate-400 mt-4">
            By booking an appointment, you agree to our <a href="/privacy" class="underline hover:text-slate-600">Privacy Policy</a>. We use Calendly to schedule calls.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Right Column: Sidebar -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-1 flex flex-col gap-8">
          
          <!-- Contact Box -->
          <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm text-center">
            <img src="/images/founders.png" alt="Leonard and Manoli" class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 object-cover object-top border-4 border-white shadow-sm" />
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Direct contact</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-6">Talk directly to the founders</p>
            
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <a href="mailto:info@taxomade.com" class="flex items-center justify-center w-full py-3 px-4 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl text-slate-700 font-medium hover:bg-slate-50 hover:border-slate-300 transition-colors">
                <span class="mr-2">✉️</span> info@taxomade.com
              </a>
              <a href="https://wa.me/35799123456" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex items-center justify-center w-full py-3 px-4 bg-[#25D366]/10 border border-[#25D366]/20 rounded-xl text-[#1DA851] font-bold hover:bg-[#25D366]/20 transition-colors">
                <span class="mr-2">💬</span> WhatsApp us
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- What to expect -->
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">What to expect</h3>
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="flex">
                <div class="shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4">1</div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Personal introduction</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">A relaxed one-on-one conversation. We listen closely and talk with you directly, founder to founder.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex">
                <div class="shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4">2</div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Clarity & strategy</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">We check whether your plan is legally and tax-wise feasible in your target country.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex">
                <div class="shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4">3</div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Your roadmap</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">After the call, you'll know exactly how the bureaucratic process will look.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Mini FAQ -->
          <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">FAQ</h3>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-sm mb-1">Is the consultation free?</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Yes, completely free and non-binding.</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-sm mb-1">Do I need documents ready?</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">No, we look at your plan strategically first.</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-sm mb-1">Am I committed after the call?</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">No. You decide afterwards, at your own pace, whether you'd like us to help.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
      
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
